Package: sonaRnetcdf4
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-02-25
Title: Tools to Read and Write netCDF4 Files in the SONAR-netCDF4 Convension
Authors@R: c(
  person(given = "Arne Johannes", 
    family = "Holmin", 
    role = c("cre", "aut"), 
    email = "arnejh@hi.no"), 
  person(given = "Norwegian Institute of Marine Research", 
    role = c("cph", "fnd")))
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Description: Functions to read and write netCDF4 files in the SONAR-netCDF4 convension,
  which is a standard for SONAR and echosounder data and derived data defined
  by the International Council for the Exploration of the Sea (ICES).
URL: https://github.com/arnejohannesholmin/sonaRnetcdf4
BugReports: https://github.com/arnejohannesholmin/sonaRnetcdf4/issues
